This project is a fork of zsh-you-should-use by Michael Aquilina
Original project: https://github.com/MichaelAquilina/zsh-you-should-use

Major enhancements in this fork include:
- Improved alias matching algorithm to find the most specific match
- Alias discovery feature to show related aliases
- Bug fixes and performance improvements

